{"title":"梦中重游天台山","authors":["郑经生"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中重游天台山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑经生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年我亦上天台，阮肇仙踪照眼开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾得有诗题石壁，丰千饶舌惹尘埃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风华顶游人醉，飞瀑悬梁倦鸟回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日离情千万种，夜深都到梦中来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载1月15日《台湾新生报》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}